    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 V&V 40 factors and determined that the overall body of evidence supports an assurance level of High. Twelve of thirteen factors meet or exceed their required levels. The single deficiency in Test conditions (achievedLevel 1 vs. requiredLevel 3) was noted but judged by the team to be offset by the strong performance across all other factors and the conservative nature of the ASTM F1717 protocol. The model is accepted for use in support of the regulatory submission.",
